        "name": "Mean-Centered CF",
        "latex": "$$\\hat{r}_{uj} = \\mu_u + \\frac{\\sum_{v} sim(u,v)(r_{vj} - \\mu_v)}{\\sum_{v} \\lvert sim(u,v) \\rvert}$$"
